          i.huge.grey.user.circle.icon
          h1.ui.header Avatar
          p
            | In E-Scooter, everyone can customize their intelligent virtual avatar. Users can not only decide avatars&apos; genders and colors but also dress them up.
        #app_col12.column(data-aos='fade-down')
          i.huge.grey.calendar.alternate.icon
